## Creating Tabs

Once you have a tab, use its methods to create UI elements. The first tab is automatically selected.

```lua
local Tab = Window:CreateTab("Main")
Tab:CreateLabel("Welcome!")
Tab:CreateButton("Click me!", function()
    print("Button pressed!")
end)
```

