## Notifications

Notifications appear in the bottom-right corner and auto-dismiss after a duration.

```lua
Window:Notify("Operation successful!", "success", 3)
Window:Notify("An error occurred!", "error", 4)
Window:Notify("Warning: Action irreversible", "warning", 3)
Window:Notify("Information for you", "info", 3)
```

**Styles:**
- `"success"` — Green accent
- `"error"` — Red accent
- `"warning"` — Orange accent
- `"info"` — White accent

