## Theme System

The library uses a comprehensive dark theme with customizable colors.

### Available Theme:
- **"Dark"** — Premium dark theme (currently only option)

### Theme Colors (customizable via source):

| Color | Purpose |
|-------|---------|
| `Background` | Main window background |
| `Surface` | Top bar, sidebar background |
| `Element` | UI element background |
| `ElementHover` | Element on hover |
| `Border` | Default border color |
| `BorderFocus` | Border when focused |
| `Input` | Input field background |
| `Accent` | Primary accent (buttons, toggles) |
| `TextPrimary` | Main text color |
| `TextSecondary` | Secondary text |
| `TextMuted` | Muted/disabled text |
| `Success` / `Error` / `Warning` | Notification colors |

