## Advanced Features

### Window Dragging
- Drag the top bar to move the window around the screen
- Smooth lerp-based dragging for fluid motion

### Window Minimize
- Click the minimize button (−) to collapse the window to just the top bar
- Click again to expand

### Window Close
- Click the close button (×) to destroy the entire UI and clean up all connections

### Auto-Responsive Layout
- Elements automatically resize based on content
- Scrollable tab content with smooth scrolling
- Toast notifications stack at the bottom-right

### Connection Management
- All event connections are tracked and cleaned up on window destruction
- No memory leaks from lingering connections

